{
  "Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: +12 % additional Attack Damage when holding a One-Handed Weapon +12 % additional Base Damage for Two-Handed Weapons": "为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 持单手武器时，额外 +12 % 攻击伤害 额外 +12 % 双手武器基础伤害",
  "Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: While standing still, +12 % additional Attack Damage and Ailment Damage dealt by attacks. -5 % additional damage taken": "为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 静止时，额外 +12 % 攻击伤害和攻击造成的 异常伤害 ，额外 -5 % 受到的伤害",
  "Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: +1 % additional Damage per +5 % Movement Speed, up to +12 %": "为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 每有 +5 % 移动速度，额外 +1 % 伤害，最多 +12 %",
  "Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: +12 % additional Attack Damage and Ailment Damage dealt by attacks when there are Elites within 10m nearby +50 % Skill Area when there are no Elites within 10m nearby": "为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 周围 10 米内有 劲敌 时，额外 +12 % 攻击伤害与攻击造成的 异常伤害 周围 10 米内没有 劲敌 时， +50 % 技能范围",
  "Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: Eliminates enemies with less than 12 % Life and at least 30 stack(s) of Wilt when dealing damage": "为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 造成伤害时，淘汰生命值低于 12 % 且至少拥有 30 层凋零的敌人",
  "Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: When channeling Harmonious Field, triggers the Sentry Main Skill if there are no Sentries within 10m. Interval: 1s +30 % Empower Skill Effect for Harmonious Field": "为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 引导调谐力场时，如果周围 10 米内没有哨卫，则触发哨卫核心技能，间隔 1 秒 +30 % 调谐力场的激发技能效果",
  "Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: Blinds enemies within 15 m when casting Dazzling Bloom +12 % additional damage for Spirit Magi against Blinded enemies": "为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 释放夺目绽放时，对 15 米内的敌人施加 致盲 魔灵对 致盲 的敌人，额外 +12 % 伤害",
  "Adds an additional effect to the Core Talent on the God of Might/Goddess of Hunting/Goddess of Knowledge/God of War/Goddess of Deception/God of Machines Advanced Talent Panel: For every stack of Max Spell Burst , +4 % additional Spell Damage, up to +16 % additional Spell Damage": "为 巨力之神/狩猎之神/知识之神/征战之神/欺诈之神/机械之神 进阶天赋板的核心天赋附加额外效果： 每有 1 层 法术迸发 上限，额外 +4 % 法术伤害，最多额外 +16 % 法术伤害",
